==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skiving
<hw>Ski"ving</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of paring or splitting leather or skins.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A piece made in paring or splitting leather;
specifically, the part from the inner, or flesh, side.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sklayre</ent>⟦br⟧
